programme.title: Stargate Atlantis - Misbegotten

programme.title: Stargate Atlantis - Irresistible

programme.title: Stargate Atlantis - Sateda

programme.title: Stargate Universe - Alliances

programme.title: Stargate Universe - The Hunt

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Ex Deus Machina

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Babylon

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Prototype

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - The Fourth Horseman (Part 1)

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - The Fourth Horseman (Part 2)
programme.desc: Season 9, Episode 11 As the Jaffa Gerak amasses forces to rise against them, the Stargate team races to find an antidote to stop a deadly Ori plague from becoming a devastating global pandemic. Ben Browder, Michael Shanks, Amanda Tapping, and Christopher Judge star.

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Collateral Damage
programme.desc: Season 9, Episode 12 Complications arise when lieutenant Colonel Cameron Mitchell becomes the victim of powerful and dangerous technology that allows individuals to share memories with each other. Ben Browder, Michael Shanks, Amanda Tapping, and Christopher Judge star.
